        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued July 5 at 8:20PM MDT until July 5 at 8:45PM MDT by NWS Glasgow MT</headline>
        <description>At 819 PM MDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 20 miles southwest
of Fourchette, or 24 miles south of Zortman, moving east at 35 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Expect damage to roofs, siding, and trees.

Locations impacted include...
Fourchette, Devils Creek Rec Area, Crooked Creek Rec Area, U L Bend
Rec Area, Sun Prairie, and Valentine.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
